item.title: New in studio : Komplete Kontrol S88
item.description:
New in studio : Komplete Kontrol S88

Enter a new era. The all-new Komplete Kontrol S-Series turns Komplete Instruments into a unified, intuitive, and inspiring playing experience. http://www.the-komplete-instrument.com Komplete Kontrol S-Series keyboards unite the world of Komplete software with a perfectly-integrated and luxurious hardware controller. These keyboards offer pure creative flow and a whole new way to play Komplete - this is truly the komplete instrument.
